<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2015-12-30</DATELINE><TITLE>Moving pathogen genomics out of the lab and into the clinic: what will it take?</TITLE><BODY>Pathogen genomic analysis is a potentially transformative new approach to the clinical and public-health management of infectious diseases. Health systems investing in this technology will need to build infrastructure and develop policies that ensure genomic information can be generated, shared and acted upon in a timely manner.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>